The Steam Autumn Sale 2019 is now on, with huge discounts on a wide range of popular games. The sale includes specials on more than 13,000 new and old titles, with discounts of up to 80% on offer to gamers. Well-known games such as The Witcher 3, PlayerUnknown’s Battlegrounds and Jurassic World: Evolution have been marked down. In addition to deals on single titles, Steam is also giving discounts on expansions and franchise bundles. Franchises featured in the Steam Autumn Sale include Assassin’s Creed, Batman: Arkham, Far Cry, Dark Souls, Middle-Earth, and Call of Duty. The sale is running from 26 November until 3 December. Below is a list of selected deals on games from the Steam Autumn Sale 2019. For the full catalogue of deals, visit the Steam Store. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-330283" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-640x360.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-640x360.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-600x338.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-768x432.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/01_1490346156-2060x1159-1200x675.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-330297" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ss_f5ee2fb899c32f4c627ee250949645e52161150b.0-640x427.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/ss_f5ee2fb899c32f4c627ee250949645e52161150b.0-6